data.description: Boasting with natural light, tons of builder & owner upgrades, you are sure to not be disappointed. Upon entry you'll find a flex room w/french doors to be used as an office, playroom, or anything extra space you need. Massive open living area as a combined living room, kitchen & dining area allows for everyday living/entertaining made easy. Enjoy the privacy from owner's suite being the only downstairs bedroom. Owners bath features dual sinks, garden soaking tub, tiled walk-in shower & walk-in closet. Additional 3 guest rooms located upstairs with one featuring its own private bath. Fully fenced in yard on pond w/covered patio w/grilling pad
